'''即時全球打擊'''（{{lang-en|Prompt Global Strike, PGS}}）是[[美軍|美軍]]開發的一種系統，可以於一小時內在世界任何地方進行[[精確導引武器|精確導引武器]]的[[常規武器|常規武器]][[空襲|空襲]]。<ref>{{cite news |first=Elaine |last=Grossman |title=Air Force Proposes New Strike Missile |url=http://www.military.com/features/0,15240,93616,00.html |publisher=[[Military.com|Military.com]] |date=2006-04-08 |accessdate=2012-02-02 |url-status=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130142108/http://www.military.com/features/0,15240,93616,00.html |archivedate=2012-01-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/In-the-works-A-missile-to-hit-anywhere-in-1-hr/articleshow/5857401.cms | work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]] | title=In the works: A missile to hit anywhere in 1 hr | date=2010-04-02 | accessdate=2013-06-18 | archive-date=2020-11-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109215807/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/In-the-works-A-missile-to-hit-anywhere-in-1-hr/articleshow/5857401.cms | dead-url=no }}</ref>與常規部隊相比，這種武器將使美國對迅速出現的威脅作出更迅速的反應。PGS系統在核衝突期間也可能有用，有可能取代針對多達30％的目標使用核武器。<ref>{{cite web|author=Kristensen, Hans M|url=http://www.fas.org/blog/ssp/2012/08/talks.php|title=Talks at U.S. Strategic Command and University of California San Diego|publisher=[[Federation_of_American_Scientists|Federation of American Scientists]]|date=2012-08-12|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-date=2013-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130130135100/http://www.fas.org/blog/ssp/2012/08/talks.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>PGS計劃涵蓋了許多已建立和新興的技術，包括常規的地面發射[[飛彈|飛彈]]以及空中和潛艇發射的[[超音速|超音速]]飛彈，儘管截至2018年尚未確定具體的PGS系統。

